### Transaction Microservices Module - HTTP Requests
### Port: 8097
### Transaction + Microservices Konuları (Outbox Pattern, Idempotency, Circuit Breaker)

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8097
@contentType = application/json

### Outbox Pattern testi
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/microservices/order/outbox
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "orderNumber": "ORD-001",
  "totalAmount": 1000.0
}

